### tony@arksolutions.it #########################################
IMAPAccount arksolutions
Host imappro.zoho.com
User tony@arksolutions.it
PassCmd "pass 2Areas/emails/tony@arksolutions.it"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN
CertificateFile ~/.ca-bundle.crt

IMAPStore arksolutions-remote
Account arksolutions

MaildirStore arksolutions-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/tony@arksolutions.it/
Inbox ~/Mail/tony@arksolutions.it/Inbox
Trash ~/Mail/tony@arksolutions.it/Trash

Channel arksolutions
Far :arksolutions-remote:
Near :arksolutions-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *

